Trisodium Hydrogendicarbonate Market FAQs
1. What is trisodium hydrogendicarbonate?
Trisodium hydrogendicarbonate, also known as sodium bicarbonate or baking soda, is a chemical compound with the formula Na3H(CO3)2.

